# .roadmap.disease_lung_normalization (폐 정상화)

작성: 2026-05-07
구동: 사용자 directive `/loop 5m cycle 고갈시까지 진행` + 4-disease roadmap 추가 (옵션 C — disease-axis-orthogonal)

본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 lung disease (폐 normalization) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + falsifier inventory.

폐 normalization scope:
- IPF (idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis) — fibrotic lung normalization
- COPD (chronic obstructive pulmonary disease)
- COVID-19 acute lung injury / ARDS / cytokine storm
- Asthma (severe / eosinophilic)
- Lung cancer (NSCLC / SCLC, EGFR/ALK 등 — F-disease-cancer 과 cross-link)
- α1-antitrypsin deficiency

