## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **lung normalization 의 진정한 의미** = restoration of alveolar-capillary barrier + gas exchange + mucus clearance + immune homeostasis. drug + delivery + regeneration multi-modal — 단일 quantum target 으로 X.
2. **IPF 진행 늦추는 약 (pirfenidone / nintedanib)** = lung function decline rate 절반 수준 — full normalization 아닌 progression slowing. quantum-design drug 가 단순 binding 만으로 normalization 보장 X.
3. **COVID-19 antiviral 우리 stack 에서 evidence 큼** — F-Q-6-B-real-nirmatrelvir-vqe (cycle 97) 가 nirmatrelvir VQE sub-µHa 도달. 단 isolated-molecule level; explicit Mpro pocket + Cys145 covalent reactive Sγ + nirmatrelvir warhead 의 supersystem VQE 가 binding-affinity path.
4. **CFTR ΔF508 (cystic fibrosis)** = misfolded protein corrector + potentiator; quantum 의 conformational dynamics 가 작은 ramp.
5. **acute COVID ARDS** = time-critical immunomodulation (tocilizumab, dexamethasone); quantum-design 대체 X.
6. **lung cancer (NSCLC EGFR/ALK)** = `.roadmap.disease_cancer` 와 cross-link.
7. wet-lab 없음 — in-silico only.

